{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"解密","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在密码学（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">cryptography <small>(en-US)</small></a>）领域，<strong>解密</strong>是指把密文（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Ciphertext\">ciphertext</a>）转换成明文（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Plaintext\">Plaintext</a>）的过程。</p>\n<p>解密是一个密码学原语：它通过一种称作<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher\">cipher</a>的编码技术，把加密信息转换成纯文本。正如加密一样，解密在当代密码学领域也是通过特有的算法，结合称作<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">key</a>的密钥来工作。由于算法通常是公开的，若要保证加密安全，就必须确保密钥高度保密。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Decryption/decryption.png\" alt=\"The decryption primitive.\" width=\"485\" height=\"81\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>解密是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption\">加密</a>的逆过程，如果密钥高度保密，在没有特定密钥的前提下从数学计算的角度来看，解密是很难做到的。这就取决于算法有多坚固，以及<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptanalysis\">密码分析学 <small>(en-US)</small></a>发展到了什么程度。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Encryption_and_Decryption\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">加密与解密</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"在密码学（cryptography (en-US)）领域，解密是指把密文（ciphertext）转换成明文（Plaintext）的过程。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Decryption","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Descifrado","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Déchiffrement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Decryption (復号)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Дешифрование","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/decryption","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/decryption/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption","title":"解密"}],"pageTitle":"解密 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}